                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-73" value="&lt;b&gt;PR Lifecycle (Read Execution → Raises PR → Agent Review → Auto-merge)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Read Execution&lt;/b&gt;: pod completes, posts callback {branch, head_sha, files_changed} to control plane. Pod exits.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Raises PR&lt;/b&gt;: control plane opens PR (base=main, head=feature/AOS-XX) using GitHub App #1 (author). Body rendered from ticket + plan + clarifications. Immediately enables &lt;i&gt;auto-merge&lt;/i&gt; (squash) — GH holds it armed and merges atomically once all branch-protection gates are green.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. Agent Review PR&lt;/b&gt;: control plane fetches diff via GH API, calls LLM with ticket + plan + diff. May lazily clone repo for cross-file checks. Posts a formal review via GitHub App #2 (reviewer): APPROVE or REQUEST_CHANGES. High-sev findings = inline comments inside REQUEST_CHANGES; low-sev = body of COMMENT review.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. Await GH Webhook&lt;/b&gt;: graph suspends. Branch protection requires N approvals (1 bot + 1 human) + CI green + conversations resolved. Human reviews directly on GitHub.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Terminal events (pull_request webhook):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• closed, merged=true → post_merge: JIRA Done, status=completed&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• closed, merged=false → abandon: JIRA Won&#39;t Do, status=cancelled&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• review changes_requested → re-dispatch Generate Code with feedback (same branch, dismisses stale approvals)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff8dc;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="710" y="570" width="260" height="540" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-59" value="Read Execution" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1580" y="1060" width="200" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-60" value="Context Engine" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#66CC00;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=14;dashed=1;strokeWidth=3;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="820" y="1160" width="365" height="290" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
